    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin allows users to enhance the default WP login page.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the entire <code>better-wp-login-page</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the <strong>Plugins</strong> screen (<strong>Plugins &gt; Installed Plugins</strong>).</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added the option to hide the language switcher.</li>\n<li>Added the option to add box shadow to the form box.</li>\n<li>Added the option to add border radius to the form box.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds the option to change the form footer links</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds styles to the remember password subform.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Change in the public styles enqueue method.</li>\n<li>Fixed typos in settings page.</li>\n<li>Adds the option to change the submit button text color.</li>\n<li>Now the checkbox icon adopts the accent color.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor CSS changes in public view.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed bug with language select.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
